ubarray Value II python,Maximum Total Subarray Value II Python,python leetcode\"/><link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https://algoforge.dev/problems/maximum-total-subarray-value-ii/python\"/><meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Maximum Total Subarray Value II Python Solution | AlgoForge\"/><meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Python solution for Maximum Total Subarray Value II (LeetCode #3691). Time O((n + k) * logn), space O(n).\"/><meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https://algoforge.dev/problems/maximum-total-subarray-value-ii/python\"/><meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"AlgoForge\"/><meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https://algoforge.dev/og-default.png\"/><meta property=\"og:image:width\" content=\"1200\"/><meta property=\"og:image:height\" content=\"630\"/><meta property=\"og:image:alt\" content=\"Maximum Total Subarray Value II Python Solution | AlgoForge\"/><meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\"/><meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary_large_image\"/><meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"Maximum Total Subarray Value II Python Solution | AlgoForge\"/><meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"Python solution for Maximum Total Subarray Value II (LeetCode #3691). Time O((n + k) * logn), space O(n).\"/><meta name=\"twitter:image\" content=\"https://algoforge.dev/og-default.png\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico?favicon.2vob68tjqpejf.ico\" sizes=\"256x256\" type=\"image/x-icon\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0cz1d0mv5g_q7.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"geist_deef94d5-module__Sms4YG__variable geist_mono_1bf8cbf6-module__FlyLvG__variable antialiased\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><script>((a,b,c,d,e,f,g,h)=>{let i=document.documentElement,j=[\"light\",\"dark\"];function k(b){var c;(Array.isArray(a)?a:[a]).forEach(a=>{let c=\"class\"===a,d=c&&f?e.map(a=>f[a]||a):e;c?(i.classList.remove(...d),i.classList.add(f&&f[b]?f[b]:b)):i.setAttribute(a,b)}),c=b,h&&j